
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="index.css">
        <title>NIEAP - Welcome</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>NeighborImpact Energy Assistance Program</h1>
        <h1>Online Application</h1>
        <p>Welcome to NeighborImpact's online application for the federal Low Income Home Energy Assistance Program ('LIHEAP'). Here we will walk you through your submitting your application.</p>
        <div class="form-group">
            <button id="ReturningUser" class="btn btn-primary">Returning User</button>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <button id="NewUser" class="btn btn-primary">New User</button>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <button id="BackHome" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Home</button>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
<script>
    document.getElementById("ReturningUser").addEventListener("click", function(){window.location.href="users/sign_in"});
    document.getElementById("NewUser").addEventListener("click", function(){window.location.href="users/sign_up"});
    document.getElementById("BackHome").addEventListener("click", function(){window.location.href="http://www.neighborimpact.org"});
</script>
